        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Scores of &ge;13 suggests minor head injury.</li>\n<li>Score of 9-12 suggests moderate head injury.</li>\n<li>Score of &le;8 suggests severe head injury.</li>\n</ul>",
